Package: DatawRappr
Type: Package
Title: Provides access to Datawrapper's API to create and edit charts directly out of R.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Benedict Witzenberger
Maintainer: Benedict Witzenberger <benedict.witzenberger@sueddeutsche.de>
Description: This package is a simple implementation to create and edit charts via Datawrapper's API.
    It makes heavy use of the _httr_-library and tries to manage the API-token for the user in the .Renviron-file.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
      httr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.99.9001
